Definition: pertaining to or resembling or befitting Faust or Faustus especially in insatiably striving for worldly knowledge and power even at the price of spiritual values
Example: a Faustian pact with the Devil
Synonyms: noun, person, faust, Faust, pertaining, to, or, resembling, befitting, Faustus, especially, in, insatiably, striving, for, worldly, knowledge, and, power, even, at, the, price, of, spiritual, values, a, pact, with, Devil
Category: adj.pert
